In [10]:
Cumul_EOL_R0 = []
Cumul_EOL_R50 = []

foo=0
foo2=0
for life in range (0, len(filter_col)):
    foo +=  r1.scenario['Repair_0'].data[filter_col[life]].iloc[0]
    foo2 += r1.scenario['Repair_50'].data[filter_col[life]].iloc[0]
    Cumul_EOL_R0.append(foo)
    Cumul_EOL_R50.append(foo2)
